Smith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hillary_B._Smith 0 Hillary Bailey Smith (born May 25, 1957) is an American actress, best known for her daytime soap opera roles as Margo Hughes on As the World Turns and Nora Hanen Buchanan on One Life to Live.
